msgctxt "60"
msgid "*huff* *huff* Shinada!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84"
msgid "Got a favor to ask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96"
msgid "What? Now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108"
msgid "When ya get to the Dome, ya might come across a guy called Baba."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120"
msgid "Baba?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132"
msgid "Yeah. He's the guy workin' for Kurosawa that planned my prison break."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144"
msgid "What's the favor?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156"
msgid "If ya see him, tell him I'll be waitin' for him here as long as it takes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168"
msgid "Huh? What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180"
msgid "I promised we'd swear an oath of brotherhood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192"
msgid "Wait, really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204"
msgid ""
"He's still young. Gotta smack some sense into that head of his, or who "
"knows what he'll get himself into."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216"
msgid "So I'm hopin' you can save not just Haruka, but Baba, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228"
msgid "Man, the lengths you guys go to for each other is just crazy sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240"
msgid "Huh? You say somethin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252"
msgid "Never mind. Anyway, first we've got to take care of the enemy at hand!"
msgstr ""

